We're thrilled to see OpenLiteracy mentioned in Education Week's latest article on how organizations are reshaping the future of education with generative AI. üöÄ

We're proud to lead the way in education innovation, combining high-impact 1:1 tutoring with AI-driven curriculum solutions to empower students and educators. Our goal: to help 1 million students learn to read within the next decade.

A huge thank you to NewSchools, who is supporting our work this year and is always at the forefront of championing transformative work in education.
